    <template>If you prefer working with hardware over software, then perhaps looking into the field of computer hardware engineering could be a great fit for you. For more information on this
    career path please
    
    <link>
        <text> click here!</text>
        <url>https://www.careerexplorer.com/careers/computer-hardware-engineer/</url>
    </link>
    
    </template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>SETUP</pattern>
    <template>Setting up the hardware to get computers/servers in a functioning state, as well as running the necessary cables to allow for networking and communication is a very important role.
    If this </template>
