        <link>
            <text> click here</text>
            <url>https://www.careerexplorer.com/careers/web-developer/</url>
        </link>
    </template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>LOGIC</pattern>
    <template>If you enjoy the logic puzzles that come with coding, take a look at the field of back-end, or server-side, programming. To learn more about this career path and whether it would be a good
